spec_data.Name: php-pear-Console-Table
spec_data.Description:
Provides methods such as addRow(), insertRow(), addCol() etc. to build
console tables with or without headers and with user defined table rules
and padding.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:48:27 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Class that makes it easy to build console style tables
